Class FieldInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • others.FieldInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccessFlags

    public class FieldInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements AccessFlags
    A class that models Fields of Java Classes. Very similar to the Method class.
